


WARNING !!!!

   First - build - pkgmk -d libxcrypt

   Update man-pages

   After updating glibc without libcrypt,
   install libxcrypt - pkgadd libcrypt#4.4.36.....

   !!!! Do not restart the computer under any circumstances. !!!!
   !!!! It is very likely that you will not log in to the system !!!!

   Run revdep and all ports like perl, linux-pam, shadow, fcron, inetutils,
   python3, util-linux, openssh, ruby ...., it is necessary to rebuild.

   Update passwd root, user.
